.IP "\s-1VYY\s0" 11
.IX Item "VYY"
(output) REAL*8, \s-1DIMENSION\s0(2*LMAX+2, 2*LMAX+2) \fIor\fR
(output) REAL*8, \s-1DIMENSION\s0(2*LMAX+2, 4*LMAX+4)
.Sp
A 2D equally sampled or equally spaced grid of the \s-1YY\s0 component of the gravity tensor.
